Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,当时的开发者已经很难把屏幕上的UI和对应的代码联系起来，并理解代码的作用\Ncomplexity wise and just the developers ability to hold in their head and understand a bit of code that somebody else wrote and you know look at the screen and say okay this code is doing that and I need to know why
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Jordan有很多有趣的想法，比如对于Blot的函数式使用\Nand Jordan had a lot of very interesting ideas around how you could take what we had done in both and make it much more functional
